- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper compares two standard supervised learning methods. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possibility as WSD is relevant to information retrieval tasks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility as WSD is a subfield of AI. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is less likely as the paper does not mention the use of neural networks or evolutionary algorithms.
